<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The title bar displays the <strong>user ID</strong> and <strong>user name</strong> as well as the <strong>date</strong> and <strong>time</strong> when changes were last made to the user account.<br>
The user ID is a unique identification number. It is assigned by the system and cannot be changed.</p></td>
