<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the user class for the user account. You can choose from the following classes: <strong>Admin</strong>, <strong>Variable</strong>, <strong>Call centre</strong>, <strong>API</strong>, <strong>Logistics</strong>, <strong>Blog</strong> and <strong>Newsletter2Go</strong>.</p></td>
</tr>
