<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Roles</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select roles for the user account. <a href="/en/basics/working-with-plentymarkets/manage-users#70">Roles</a> must have already been created before they can be selected here.</p></td>
</tr>
