<div class="paragraph">
<p>The maximum number of login attempts is 5 per user account or 25 per IP address. If the maximum number of login attempts was exceeded, then the following message will be displayed: You have exceeded the maximum number of invalid login attempts. Your account has been temporarily locked. In such a case, a new login attempt can first be carried out after 24 hours.</p>
</div>
