</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>My account</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Email</strong> tab.<br>
→ A list of the mailboxes is displayed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the mailbox in this list that you want to delete.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Delete</strong>.<br>
→ The mailbox and all associated aliases are deleted on the mailbox.org server.<br>
→ Your plentymarkets contract is updated.</p>
</li>
